description: Redevelopment of the site involving the demolition of the existing building and the erection of a 23 storey building (including basement) to contain 1770 square metres (GEA) of commercial floorspace (flexible use for B1 or A2) together with 101 self contained flats (41 x 1 bed, 44 x 2 bed, 8 x 3 bed, 4 x 4 bed and 4 x 5 bed) on upper floors
